description:
In this episode Walter and Sonica Veith talk about events around Walters first evangelistic campaigns and the many signs of the spiritual warfare they were caught up in. 

Why did God allow them to go through so many trials when they were doing His work? The Veiths reflect on the challenges, the miracles and the lessons they learned as Walter Veith entered ministry. Hear their convictions about the importance of being in constant prayer.

For more lectures please visit:
http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/c/22/Walter_Veith/

Visit our website: http://amazingdiscoveries.org
